## What & why
The weave client computes object digests CLIENT-SIDE
(weave_client.py:2276/2293 compute_object_digest -> ObjCreateReq.expected_digest;
the server validates it). So the client is a distinct producer worth its own
conformance consumer. test_conformance_client.py publishes the corpus's plain
object_digest rows via weave.publish and asserts ObjectRef.digest == corpus
digest. Trust chain: client==corpus + server==corpus + (future) ts==corpus =>
all producers agree.

